   *  - {string} A css selector
   *  - {HTMLElement} A single element
   * -  {NodeList} A NodeList or collection
   *  - {HTMLElement[]} An array of Elements
   * -  {Array<HTMLElement|NodeList|HTMLElement[]>} A nested array of elements
